snippet.title: Abducted Toad FINAL GAME Trailer!
snippet.description:
Here's a new trailer for Abducted Toad!  The game is very close to completion!  The full game is coming soon!
Featuring original music by the awesome K16/AngryLemon!  Go check out his channel over here:
